dmca.title: Blogger DMCA Complaint- Real Big Networks
dmca.body:
To: Google, Inc. 
Attn: Blogger Legal Support, DMCA complaints 
I am submitting a complaint based on the DMCA, as follows: 
SECTION 1. Identify in sufficient detail the copyrighted work that you believe has been infringed upon. 
1. More Web2.0 Newspaper Links Than Anyone Could Ever Want 
http://www.web2.0television.com/blog/2006/11/07/more-web20newspaper-links-than-anyone- could-ever-want/

2. Digg dustup only reinforces Shirky
